rmal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69110ac03400ed425439770fc9c80f7b07f17a58","tid":319453,"uid":71695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:38:41.000Z","msg":"巴打加油"},{"pid":"37685bc50526419426a51f14d88941858c618634","tid":319453,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗掉既，收好save好d野，等你重新鎮作既時候先再拎返出黎，一齊咁耐經歷得多掛住好正常，但我諗佢唔會想你為佢而頹廢，如果佢知道佢一定會好唔開心<br />\n加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagree"},{"pid":"145a0ebc8900dd6bdbe14ce7848a6a9ed66ef2cf","tid":319453,"uid":75764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:43:48.000Z","msg":"感動了 加油"},{"pid":"ee061cdeaf6694865dc3c8b0a9051a412894f533","tid":319453,"uid":52903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:56:51.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"2dc85154b569409b2e2cfc05d100393141ab3fb9","tid":319453,"uid":96732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:57:08.000Z","msg":"加油呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9027a073372489fed8937c6d0d4d14b9964b91a","tid":319453,"uid":127337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T19:58:59.000Z","msg":"巴打加油"},{"pid":"db13c5d81f7c7a86b1b98fe99521744fa1f8a447","tid":319453,"uid":66965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T20:39:47.000Z","msg":"都唔知應該比正皮定係負皮好<br />\n比正皮即係好似之前你掉晒啲嘢<br />\n但係比負皮我有諗唔到有啲咩原因要比<br />\nBtw 樓主唔好掉晒啲嘢<br />\n因為啲嘢可以俾你懷緬下過去<br />\n當係佢仲存在嘅一個證明"},{"pid":"2866e20ecbcca0cf7d44636420a075ac4622d632","tid":319453,"uid":117629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:26:51.000Z","msg":"樓主要加油<br />\n我同你差唔多 <br />\n一年前男朋友車禍過左身<br />\n到而家都仲未肯放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7015c4fbdbeeaa266d511e142c793d3c7801041","